msgid ""
"The script uses **PSPG only** (no SUPG), with a constant :math:`\\tau = "
"0.05 / n_\\text{grid}`. At :math:`\\mathrm{Ra} = 10^4` the velocities are"
" mild enough that SUPG is not strictly required; for higher Rayleigh "
"numbers, swap in the adaptive :math:`\\tau` from :doc:`cylinder_flow`."
msgstr ""

