"characteristic warm rising plumes / cool sinking plumes) and velocity "
"magnitude (with the two-roll structure). For a 2:1 cavity at moderate "
":math:`\\mathrm{Ra}` the steady solution features two counter-rotating "
"rolls."
msgstr ""

